11 beginning July 1, 2027, and ending June 30, 2028, the following discrete sums, or so
12 much thereof as may be necessary. Appropriated funds are included pursuant to KRS
13 48.700 and 48.710. Each appropriation is made by source of respective fund or funds
14 accounts. Appropriations for the budget units of the Transportation Cabinet are subject to
